nodes.text: Jessica Henwick (born August 30, 1992) is an English actress who played Jessika Pava in Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens. She is also known for playing Nymeria Sand in Game of Thrones, and Colleen Wing in the Netflix series Iron Fist, The Defenders and the second season of Luke Cage, based on the Marvel Comics character.

Henwick was a finalist for the role of Rey in The Force Awakens, and auditioned for six months. She expressed interest in reprising the role as Jessika Pava for the 2019 film Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker, but her character did not make an appearance in the film.
